{"tid":218203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"棒球JJ入一入黎","createTime":"2017-04-26T10:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T11:47:09.000Z","uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"262e5a5f466aa532b8227da308f6492e491222ca","tid":218203,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:31:23.000Z","msg":"1) 一壘有runner果陣, 係投手投球之前, 個runner偷跑去二壘, 投手發現左之後, 投去二壘定一壘先可以out左個runner? 投去三疊又得唔得?<br />\n<br />\n2)係二壘有人果陣,投手投好球之後, 擊球手打出高空球 然後守方係個波落地前接住, 咁個擊球手係咪out左? 定係係個波俾人接之前, 跑過去一壘就唔會out?  守方接到個波 ，咁本身二壘個runner會唔會out?<br />\n<br />\n3)如果一局入面攻方係咁擊球上壘無人OUT, 咁係咪可以係咁拎分, 唔會攻守交換? <br />\n<br />\n4) 當一壘有runner A, 二壘有runner B, A跑去二壘 B跑去三壘. 要雙殺佢地既話, 係咪投個波去二壘 之後再二壘投去三壘? 洗唔洗用個波掂runner?<br />\n投手又係投左俾捕手 再捕手投去二壘<br />\n定可以直接投俾二壘？"},{"pid":"671c3c24d31fa8a92dea8b4f402b554f827d1b97","tid":218203,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce8c3d32f36fd5ddc46f655005cbb59f4396eff","tid":218203,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2794c991ed3ed7d9a57bfe6b30e7397b02903c6","tid":218203,"uid":99907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"1) 投手要投去一壘 呢d叫做牽制 如果投手投左個波出去 捕手就要投去二壘 封殺佢個盜壘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bfb4995bf5026ac5b4550993cdae2ffdab7272d","tid":218203,"uid":99907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:43:08.000Z","msg":"2） 擊球手打高空波出去 波落地前比守方接到 咁佢就直接out， 而二壘個runner就唔會比人out假設佢無嘗試去偷三壘。 如果佢嘗試去盜三壘 咁守方就可以投去三疊手 睇下可唔可以觸殺佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e2b44a9db78aa40958bfb66858a5a9ca617a75","tid":218203,"uid":99907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:43:46.000Z","msg":"3) 無錯 一局入面 有三個out 先會攻守交換"},{"pid":"ef16ef1ed1617cca965245e69904f2839a48e4a0","tid":218203,"uid":99907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"4)  要觸殺攻方 係守方球員個手套掂到runner, 而唔係個波掂到。 正常係投比三疊先 再投比二疊。 因為三疊重要過二疊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然你可以投比二疊先 再投比三疊 但唔會咁做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08b2c80accad637fc0d266d084d8e02aefdeb87","tid":218203,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:47:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1) 投手要投去一壘 呢d叫做牽制 如果投手投左個波出去 捕手就要投去二壘 封殺佢個盜壘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牽制既話 一壘係咪要拎個波掂到runner先out到佢？"},{"pid":"2b618586fc4a8bab937ee70cccd053a473e5ce99","tid":218203,"uid":99907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:49:10.000Z","msg":"4) 投手點直接投比二疊 係佢正後方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋runner盜疊前 係要等投手開始左投球動作之後 先可以盜 如果runner離疊好遠 投手想牽制 就投球前投比疊手做牽制 睇下可唔可以觸殺佢"},{"pid":"c45851c9ab27df58dbefd89e33ea99467b00334c","tid":218203,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4)  要觸殺攻方 係守方球員個手套掂到runner, 而唔係個波掂到。 正常係投比三疊先 再投比二疊。 因為三疊重要過二疊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然你可以投比二疊先 再投比三疊 但唔會咁做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手套掂到 咁係咪都要條友拎住個波？"},{"pid":"cf66829f43655e09f2b3808c358c044d21fc333e","tid":218203,"uid":99907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1) 投手要投去一壘 呢d叫做牽制 如果投手投左個波出去 捕手就要投去二壘 封殺佢個盜壘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牽制既話 一壘係咪要拎個波掂到runner先out到佢？</blockquote><br />\n永遠係疊手接實個波 再用手套掂到個runner 先叫觸殺"},{"pid":"875edbcedf30ad69c3d80bead99855ee0cac8304","tid":218203,"uid":99907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:50:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4)  要觸殺攻方 係守方球員個手套掂到runner, 而唔係個波掂到。 正常係投比三疊先 再投比二疊。 因為三疊重要過二疊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然你可以投比二疊先 再投比三疊 但唔會咁做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手套掂到 咁係咪都要條友拎住個波？</blockquote><br />\n無錯 前提下係要接實個波先"},{"pid":"59a5e457e47b9661bab1e6ad64b25371d06f6419","tid":218203,"uid":99907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:51:19.000Z","msg":"利申無打過棒球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇哂棒球大聯盟 1-6季 無限次既JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1432f9ada419389ce6f1f95ce6024ba9285db973","tid":218203,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:53:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4) 投手點直接投比二疊 係佢正後方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋runner盜疊前 係要等投手開始左投球動作之後 先可以盜 如果runner離疊好遠 投手想牽制 就投球前投比疊手做牽制 睇下可唔可以觸殺佢</blockquote><br />\n向後掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你離好遠既意思係個runner行左去紅色邊位 想跑，所以就試下投俾壘手觸殺佢？runner唔跑 仍然係紅色位入面 咁觸唔觸殺得？"},{"pid":"38f8fd17d2cd673f8f9223c46d8f9e52646440bd","tid":218203,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:54:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申無打過棒球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇哂棒球大聯盟 1-6季 無限次既JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8046a4d484f296dab86bd01baef7274e000601b9","tid":218203,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:54:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3) 無錯 一局入面 有三個out 先會攻守交換</blockquote><br />\n咁咪可以唔完場"},{"pid":"09d99f5d2e2df7b7b80fd5be0b7a5cf2a5a0411b","tid":218203,"uid":22259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1) 一壘有runner果陣, 係投手投球之前, 個runner偷跑去二壘, 投手發現左之後, 投去二壘定一壘先可以out左個runner? 投去三疊又得唔得?<br />\n<br />\n2)係二壘有人果陣,投手投好球之後, 擊球手打出高空球 然後守方係個波落地前接住, 咁個擊球手係咪out左? 定係係個波俾人接之前, 跑過去一壘就唔會out?  守方接到個波 ，咁本身二壘個runner會唔會out?<br />\n<br />\n3)如果一局入面攻方係咁擊球上壘無人OUT, 咁係咪可以係咁拎分, 唔會攻守交換? <br />\n<br />\n4) 當一壘有runner A, 二壘有runner B, A跑去二壘 B跑去三壘. 要雙殺佢地既話, 係咪投個波去二壘 之後再二壘投去三壘? 洗唔洗用個波掂runner?<br />\n投手又係投左俾捕手 再捕手投去二壘<br />\n定可以直接投俾二壘？</blockquote><br />\n1. Tag到先死<br />\n2. Fly ball跑到邊個擊球手都out, fly ball既話二壘個人一定要接左先可以起跑 如果fly左 你二壘個人偷跑左既話個波快過你返到二壘都要out<br />\n3. 係 但拎太多分好似有mercy rule會cut game<br />\n4. 如果係batter擊出既話 Force run唔洗tag 不過係先扔三壘殺二壘runner 再掉二壘殺一壘runner<br />\n如果係三振batter runner都跑就要tag先會死 當偷壘咁殺"},{"pid":"d329a1ca51de7493c3c0d77a9cc0425fd5233a53","tid":218203,"uid":174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:14:12.000Z","msg":"3. 職棒一般都係。香港打個d 有9 batter 制，打完第九個就攻守互換"},{"pid":"a17097240c741a4e901c8c2941ff16a85e62a374","tid":218203,"uid":3401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:41:45.000Z","msg":"先了解一下觸殺 接殺 封殺先會比較容易理解"},{"pid":"0d54f52ac8cbe1020eec3bb81771fb3c91646749","tid":218203,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1) 一壘有runner果陣, 係投手投球之前, 個runner偷跑去二壘, 投手發現左之後, 投去二壘定一壘先可以out左個runner? 投去三疊又得唔得?<br />\n<br />\n2)係二壘有人果陣,投手投好球之後, 擊球手打出高空球 然後守方係個波落地前接住, 咁個擊球手係咪out左? 定係係個波俾人接之前, 跑過去一壘就唔會out?  守方接到個波 ，咁本身二壘個runner會唔會out?<br />\n<br />\n3)如果一局入面攻方係咁擊球上壘無人OUT, 咁係咪可以係咁拎分, 唔會攻守交換? <br />\n<br />\n4) 當一壘有runner A, 二壘有runner B, A跑去二壘 B跑去三壘. 要雙殺佢地既話, 係咪投個波去二壘 之後再二壘投去三壘? 洗唔洗用個波掂runner?<br />\n投手又係投左俾捕手 再捕手投去二壘<br />\n定可以直接投俾二壘？</blockquote><br />\n1. Tag到先死<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. Fly ball跑到邊個擊球手都out, fly ball既話二壘個人一定要接左先可以起跑 如果fly左 你二壘個人偷跑左既話個波快過你返到二壘都要out</span><br />\n3. 係 但拎太多分好似有mercy rule會cut game<br />\n4. 如果係batter擊出既話 Force run唔洗tag 不過係先扔三壘殺二壘runner 再掉二壘殺一壘runner<br />\n如果係三振batter runner都跑就要tag先會死 當偷壘咁殺</blockquote><br />\n咁二壘個runner 偷跑左 快過個波去到3壘呢？<br />\n一定要接左波先可以跑？<br />\n唔係fly波又洗唔洗接左先跑"},{"pid":"3e79199d4d122c79567e92dbc3f014cbc0211e8b","tid":218203,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先了解一下觸殺 接殺 封殺先會比較容易理解</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n封殺：屬於強迫進壘狀態，防守球員只需採壘包即可讓跑者出局，例如在一 壘有跑者時，打者擊出滾地球，防守球員接到傳向二壘，或是滿壘時，傳向 本壘，皆是屬於封殺的動作<br />\n<br />\n點解唔洗掂條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為滾地球？"},{"pid":"716bd3c9a4f5f9b7d8a66b0a200969e7afe24e1b","tid":218203,"uid":99907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"去睇下 棒球大聯盟 呢套動畫/漫畫 就會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b72dc129364cf98dce1c891661dc027aee6033","tid":218203,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:29:21.000Z","msg":"我做左廿幾年人都唔知棒球點玩 好失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc047a8f2947f4b14374bfc26380df16b2b6372c","tid":218203,"uid":99907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>先了解一下觸殺 接殺 封殺先會比較容易理解</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n封殺：屬於強迫進壘狀態，防守球員只需採壘包即可讓跑者出局，例如在一 壘有跑者時，打者擊出滾地球，防守球員接到傳向二壘，或是滿壘時，傳向 本壘，皆是屬於封殺的動作<br />\n<br />\n點解唔洗掂條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為滾地球？</blockquote><br />\n其實掂唔掂到條友唔係重點 只要你接實個波+踩住個壘包果時 快過個runner踩個壘包 runner已經要out<br />\n<br />\n至於咩情況要掂個對手 就係 當三壘有人 佢地強迫搶分，姐係3壘要盜本壘 而捕手識穿左 叫個投手投壞球 咁個runner跑黎本疊 捕手就要用手套掂個runner 就觸殺佢出局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd928c48bdbfede6878c5a1b06be9d665c2d786","tid":218203,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我做左廿幾年人都唔知棒球點玩 好失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}